{"tid":1008390,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"賀年糕點分享(蘿蔔糕)","createTime":"2019-02-04T12:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T12:52:03.000Z","uid":222613,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"734ae533fb5e09495180d0068fca2546e787e0ce","tid":1008390,"uid":222613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"雖則我認為都無咩人有興趣自己整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n但新年無聊既不妨試下整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n材料:<br />\n粘米粉1斤4兩、澄麵2兩、栗粉2兩、馬啼粉1兩、水6斤<br />\n鹽1兩、味 2兩、糖3兩<br />\n蘿白絲4斤、蝦米，瑤柱，臘腸，冬茹粒，叉燒粒全部適量<br />\n做法:<br />\n1.全部粉同調味料溝埋，加3斤凍水撈埋<br />\n2.蘿白絲飛水，倒入以上糊狀，再加3斤熱水<br />\n3.全部配料落油炒炒佢，倒入以上糊狀，用力撈至全部野埋<br />\n4.大火蒸1小時,等佢冷卻後，第2日就可以切黎煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGhHnVV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGhHnVV.jpg&h=2a6d0455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOYb0HA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOYb0HA.jpg&h=07fa6aab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yx87y2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyx87y2A.jpg&h=0da8cd24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMPuNnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMPuNnB.jpg&h=c3ac7a59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac2ae1248f8c2cd662795093ad4afa26b9aecf4c","tid":1008390,"uid":4458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0d95be84235b973825d1200339ca9021572585","tid":1008390,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"734ae533fb5e09495180d0068fca2546e787e0ce","tid":1008390,"uid":222613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2